

Requisição HTTP

URL: `https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokemon`
    ${IP}/${path = caminho de idenfificação do recurso}

IP: https://pokeapi.co

Request Method: GET | POST | DELETE | PATCH 


`https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokemon/${id}`
`https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokemon/1`
`https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokemon/2`
`https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokemon/3`


pokemon do tipo grama e nomes iniciados em i :
`https://pokeapi.co/api/v2/pokemon?type=grass&name=i`

type = grass
name = i


Request Headers
    Configuração
    Autorization:

Response Headers
    Configuração
    content-type:application/json

Request Body

Body
{
"name":"Teste"
}

**STATUS CODE** :significa o que aconteceu com nossa requisição - 200 ok

